{
  "texts": [
    "Future research should focus on developing more robust and generalizable AI models by leveraging larger and more diverse datasets.",
    "Collaborative efforts across institutions can help in creating comprehensive databases that enhance the training and validation of AI systems.",
    "Furthermore, establishing clear guidelines for the development, validation, and deployment of AI tools in orthodontics will be crucial for ensuring their safe and effective use in the clinical setting.When interpreting the results of the present study, some limitations should be addressed.",
    "The search strategy, although open and broad, may not have included the entirety of the literature available on the topic.",
    "However, the inclusion of the keyword \"Orthodontic*\" in the search strategy should have allowed the inclusion of the majority of relevant articles."
  ]
}